article_id:845,category_name:News,title_name:Special Halloween Weapons for All Participants of the Facility Event!,image_path:,message:<div>We are sending special Halloween to everyone playing the Trick or Treasure! facility event revival!<br>We hope these weapons will help you enjoy the event!<br><br>■Gift Content<br>・Jack-o&#39;-Lance (Lance)<br>・Vampire&#39;s Lantern (Staff)<br><br>This gift will be sent to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1572501599"></span>, and can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1571995800,update_time1571993115